// Series lookback on a `var` variable inside its own reassignment: the previous
// value must be committed to history BEFORE the RHS is evaluated, so `acc[1]`
// sees the previous bar's value. (Getting this order wrong lags every recursive
// series, e.g. Heikin-Ashi, by one bar.)

// Bars: 3
var acc = 0.0
acc := acc[1] + 1.0
log.info(str.tostring(acc))

// Expected output:
// 1
// 2
// 3
